### Some projects
* [A simple layout manager in javascript](http://yellowiscool.github.com/Cadreur/)
* [A javascript library for realtime data display](https://github.com/yellowiscool/JsCHRIST)
* [A web application about sport data visualization](https://github.com/yellowiscool/InspecteurDeryque)
* [A photo gallery using advanced web features](https://github.com/yellowiscool/XMLGallery2011)
* [A rally cars video game for blind people](http://users.polytech.unice.fr/~strombon/DEVINT2011/Projet4G2/index.html)

### More of my websites
* [Blogjaune](http://www.blogjaune.fr/)
* [My linuxfr account](http://linuxfr.org/users/yellowiscool)
* [A little of spam on social networks](http://yellowiscool.overblog.com/) _(facebook, instagramm, twitter, on one website)_
